description=KernelSU/ReSukiSU module for q5q NFC. Keeps stock libnfc-nxp.conf and provides the SN220 RF file needed by the HAL at /system/vendor/libnfc-nxp_RF.conf or /vendor/libnfc-nxp_RF.conf via a working overlayfs/Mountify setup.
